Aadil Manzoor Peer ( born 02 March ), Popularly Known as Syed Aadi, is an Indian International Icestocksport Athlete, Web Developer by Education. Syed Aadi has won many National Gold Medals and record holder for the first gold medalist in the Country and holds the distinction of having the most consistant performer in the history of indian Icestock Sport. Aadi is actie in Icestock with Right Hand style and he has represented india at international level, and J&K and Appolo teams respectively.
